{"text":"I've always liked to think of consciousness as a picture puzzle.

When the puzzle is put together you see the full picture (the mind), but the puzzle is made up of physical pieces that need to be put together (the matter).

The puzzle pieces are the neurological pathways in the brain that would process information into a quantifiable form."}

